svg.title: scene3
svg.text: Semaphores continue to disappear, logs agree but reveal little more.
Log as much semaphore activity as possible
Notice that semaphores disappear consistently on daily cron job runs
Deduce the instigating cron job through elimination (being unable to incite misbehaviour through explicit invocation).
Why does this cron job not fail when invoked explicitly?
How does a cron job which does not interact with the part of our system that is acting up, cause said part to act up?
Bionic, what are you doing that we can not see? Out with it.
